#: 
msgid "Allow visitors to create their own family record via the self-registration page"
msgstr "Laat besoekers toe om hul eie gesinsrekord te skep via die selfregistrasie-bladsy"

#: 
msgid "Allow visitors to self-register as new families."
msgstr "Laat besoekers toe om as nuwe gesinne te selfregistreer."

#. plugin:external-backup:section:5:content
#: 
msgid "Any WebDAV-compatible service works with this plugin:\n"
"\n"
"- Nextcloud (recommended)\n"
"- ownCloud\n"
"- Synology NAS\n"
"- QNAP NAS\n"
"- Box.com (with WebDAV)\n"
"- Apache mod_dav\n"
"- nginx with WebDAV module\n"
"\n"
"Note: Some services require app-specific passwords for WebDAV access."
msgstr "Enige WebDAV-versoenbare diens werk met hierdie inprop:\n"
"\n"
"- Nextcloud (aanbeveel)\n"
"- ownCloud\n"
"- Synology NAS\n"
"- QNAP NAS\n"
"- Box.com (met WebDAV)\n"
"- Apache mod_dav\n"
"- nginx met WebDAV-module\n"
"\n"
"Let wel: Sommige dienste vereis toepassing-spesifieke wagwoorde vir WebDAV-toegang."

#. plugin:openlp:section:4:title
#: 
msgid "Authentication"
msgstr "Verifikasie"

#. plugin:openlp:section:4:content
#: 
msgid "Authentication is required for API v2 if you've enabled it in OpenLP's Remote plugin settings. The plugin uses HTTP Basic Authentication. Most local network setups don't require authentication, but it's recommended for security."
msgstr "Verifikasie word vereis vir API v2 as jy dit in OpenLP se Remote-inpropinstellings geaktiveer het. Die inprop gebruik HTTP Basic Authentication. Die meeste plaaslike netwerkopstellings vereis nie verifikasie nie, maar dit word vir sekuriteit aanbeveel."

#: 
msgid "Auto TLS"
msgstr "Outomatiese TLS"

#. plugin:external-backup:section:2:title
#: 
msgid "Auto-Backup"
msgstr "Outo-rugsteun"

#: 
msgid "BCC All Mail To"
msgstr "BCC Alle Pos Aan"

#. plugin:external-backup:section:4:content
#: 
msgid "Before relying on external backups, test your connection:\n"
"1. Go to Plugins > External Backup\n"
"2. Click 'Test WebDAV Connection'\n"
"3. Verify you see a success message\n"
"\n"
"Common issues:\n"
"- 401/403 errors: Check username and password\n"
"- Connection timeout: Verify the endpoint URL is correct\n"
"- Certificate errors: Ensure the WebDAV server has a valid SSL certificate"
msgstr "Voordat jy op eksterne rugsteune staatmaak, toets jou verbinding:\n"
"1. Gaan na Inproppe > Eksterne Rugsteun\n"
"2. Klik 'Toets WebDAV-verbinding'\n"
"3. Bevestig dat jy 'n suksesboodskap sien\n"
"\n"
"Algemene probleme:\n"
"- 401/403-foute: Kontroleer gebruikersnaam en wagwoord\n"
"- Verbindingsuitteltyd: Verifieer dat die eindpunt-URL korrek is\n"
"- Sertifikaatfoute: Maak seker die WebDAV-bediener het 'n geldige SSL-sertifikaat"

