msgid "How it works"
msgstr "Hoe dit werk"

#: 
msgid "How many checks to print per deposit slip page"
msgstr "Hoeveel tjekke per depositostrokiebladsy gedruk moet word"

#. plugin:vonage:section:3:content
#: 
msgid "If SMS messages aren't being sent:\n"
"1. Verify API Key and Secret are correct (no extra spaces)\n"
"2. Check that the From Number is a valid Vonage number you own\n"
"3. Ensure recipient phone numbers include country code\n"
"4. Check your Vonage account balance\n"
"5. Review the Vonage Dashboard > SMS > Logs for delivery status"
msgstr "As SMS-boodskappe nie gestuur word nie:\n"
"1. Verifieer dat die API-sleutel en geheim korrek is (geen ekstra spasies nie)\n"
"2. Kontroleer dat die Van-nommer 'n geldige Vonage-nommer is wat jy besit\n"
"3. Maak seker dat ontvanger-telefoonnommers die landkode insluit\n"
"4. Kontroleer jou Vonage-rekeningbalans\n"
"5. Hersien die Vonage-kontroleskerm > SMS > Logs vir afleweringstatus"

#. plugin:openlp:section:5:content
#: 
msgid "If alerts aren't appearing:\n"
"1. Verify OpenLP is running and the Remote plugin is active\n"
"2. Ensure the Alerts plugin is enabled in OpenLP\n"
"3. Check that the server URL is correct (try accessing it in a browser)\n"
"4. Verify firewall settings allow connections on port 4316\n"
"5. If using authentication, verify credentials are correct"
msgstr "As waarskuwings nie verskyn nie:\n"
"1. Verifieer dat OpenLP loop en die Remote-inprop aktief is\n"
"2. Maak seker die Alerts-inprop is geaktiveer in OpenLP\n"
"3. Kontroleer dat die bediener-URL korrek is (probeer om dit in 'n blaaier oop te maak)\n"
"4. Verifieer dat brandhekkie-instellings verbindings op poort 4316 toelaat\n"
"5. As jy verifikasie gebruik, verifieer dat die geloofsbriewe korrek is"

#. plugin:vonage:section:5:content
#: 
msgid "If messages are sent but not received:\n"
"1. Check Vonage Dashboard > SMS > Logs for delivery status\n"
"2. Verify the recipient number is correct and can receive SMS\n"
"3. Some carriers may block messages from unknown numbers\n"
"4. Check if the destination country has SMS restrictions"
msgstr "As boodskappe gestuur word maar nie ontvang word nie:\n"
"1. Kontroleer Vonage-kontroleskerm > SMS > Logs vir afleweringstatus\n"
"2. Verifieer dat die ontvangernommer korrek is en SMS kan ontvang\n"
"3. Sommige diensverskaffers kan boodskappe van onbekende nommers blokkeer\n"
"4. Kontroleer of die bestemmingsland SMS-beperkings het"

#. plugin:vonage:section:4:content
#: 
msgid "If you receive invalid sender ID errors:\n"
"1. Use a phone number you've purchased from Vonage\n"
"2. Format the number in E.164 format (+14155551234)\n"
"3. Note: Alphanumeric sender IDs may be restricted in some countries"
msgstr "As jy ongeldige sender-ID-foute ontvang:\n"
"1. Gebruik 'n telefoonnommer wat jy van Vonage gekoop het\n"
"2. Formateer die nommer in E.164-formaat (+14155551234)\n"
"3. Let wel: Alfanumeriese sender-ID's kan in sommige lande beperk word"

#. plugin:external-backup:section:6:content
#: 
msgid "Important security notes:\n"
"\n"
"1. Always use HTTPS endpoints to encrypt backups in transit\n"
"2. Use app-specific passwords when available (Nextcloud, ownCloud)\n"
"3. Store backups in a folder with restricted access\n"
"4. Periodically download and verify your backups are valid\n"
"5. Consider encrypting sensitive backups with external tools before uploading"
msgstr "Belangrike sekuriteitsopmerkings:\n"
"\n"
"1. Gebruik altyd HTTPS-eindpunte om rugsteune tydens oordrag te enkripteer\n"
"2. Gebruik toepassing-spesifieke wagwoorde waar beskikbaar (Nextcloud, ownCloud)\n"
"3. Stoor rugsteune in 'n gids met beperkte toegang\n"
"4. Laai periodiek rugsteune af en verifieer dat hulle geldig is\n"
"5. Oorweeg dit om sensitiewe rugsteune met eksterne gereedskap te enkripteer voor oplaai"

