#: 
msgid "Vonage SMS API Documentation"
msgstr "Vonage SMS API-dokumentasie"

#. plugin:vonage:summary
#: 
msgid "Vonage SMS enables text message notifications for ChurchCRM using the Vonage API (formerly Nexmo). Send SMS alerts to parents when their child checks in via the kiosk system."
msgstr "Vonage SMS aktiveer teksboodskap-kennisgewings vir ChurchCRM deur die Vonage API (voorheen Nexmo) te gebruik. Stuur SMS-waarskuwings aan ouers wanneer hul kind via die kiosk-stelsel inklok."

#. plugin:vonage:section:6:content
#: 
msgid "Vonage charges per SMS sent. Pricing varies by destination country. See the Vonage pricing page for current rates. New accounts receive free trial credit for testing."
msgstr "Vonage hef per gestuurde SMS. Pryse wissel volgens bestemmingsland. Sien die Vonage-prysebladsy vir huidige tariewe. Nuwe rekeninge ontvang gratis proefkrediet vir toetsing."

#. plugin:google-analytics:section:1:title
#: 
msgid "What Gets Tracked"
msgstr "Wat Word Nagespoor"

#. plugin:mailchimp:section:3:content
#: 
msgid "When MailChimp is configured, a 'MailChimp' tab appears on Person view pages showing:\n"
"\n"
"- Email subscription status across all lists\n"
"- Which lists the person is subscribed to\n"
"- Subscription statistics"
msgstr "Wanneer MailChimp gekonfigureer is, verskyn 'n 'MailChimp'-oortjie op Persoonaansig-bladsye wat die volgende wys:\n"
"\n"
"- E-posintekenstatus oor alle lyste\n"
"- Watter lyste die persoon op ingeteken is\n"
"- Intekenstatistieke"

#. plugin:gravatar:section:0:content
#: 
msgid "When a member doesn't have an uploaded photo, ChurchCRM checks if they have a Gravatar associated with their email address. If a Gravatar exists, it displays that image. If not, the configured default image style is used."
msgstr "Wanneer 'n gemeentelid nie 'n opgelaaide foto het nie, kontroleer ChurchCRM of hulle 'n Gravatar het wat met hul e-posadres geassosieer word. As 'n Gravatar bestaan, word daardie beeld vertoon. Indien nie, word die gekonfigureerde verstekbeeldstyl gebruik."

#. plugin:external-backup:section:2:content
#: 
msgid "When auto-backup is enabled (interval > 0 hours), ChurchCRM will automatically create and upload a full database backup at the specified interval. The backup runs as part of normal page loads, so the system must have regular user activity to trigger backups.\n"
"\n"
"Recommended intervals:\n"
"- Daily backup: 24 hours\n"
"- Twice daily: 12 hours\n"
"- Weekly: 168 hours"
msgstr "Wanneer outo-rugsteun geaktiveer is (interval > 0 ure), sal ChurchCRM outomaties 'n volledige databasis-rugsteun skep en oplaai teen die gespesifiseerde interval. Die rugsteun loop as deel van normale bladsyladings, so die stelsel moet gereelde gebruikersaktiwiteit hê om rugsteune te aktiveer.\n"
"\n"
"Aanbevole intervalle:\n"
"- Daaglikse rugsteun: 24 uur\n"
"- Twee keer daagliks: 12 uur\n"
"- Weekliks: 168 uur"

#. plugin:openlp:section:1:content
#: 
msgid "When enabled and configured, ChurchCRM sends alert messages to your OpenLP server using the API v2 endpoint (POST /api/v2/plugins/alerts). These alerts appear as overlay notifications on your projected display."
msgstr "Wanneer geaktiveer en gekonfigureer, stuur ChurchCRM waarskuwingsboodskappe na jou OpenLP-bediener deur die API v2-eindpunt (POST /api/v2/plugins/alerts) te gebruik. Hierdie waarskuwings verskyn as oorlegkennisgewings op jou geprojekteerde skerm."

#: 
msgid "When enabled, hides the address field for people not assigned to a family"
msgstr "Wanneer geaktiveer, versteek dit die adresveld vir mense wat nie aan 'n gesin toegewys is nie"

#: 
msgid "When enabled, hides the latitude/longitude fields in the Family Editor. Geocoding still runs in the background."
msgstr "Wanneer geaktiveer, versteek dit die breedtegraad-/lengtegraadvelde in die Gesinsredigeerder. Geokoding loop steeds in die agtergrond."

#. plugin:external-backup:section:3:content
#: 
msgid "You can also trigger a manual backup at any time:\n"
"1. Go to the External Backup settings page (Plugins > External Backup)\n"
"2. Select backup type (Database Only or Full Backup)\n"
"3. Click 'Backup to WebDAV Now'\n"
"\n"
"Database Only backups are smaller and faster. Full backups include uploaded photos."
msgstr "Jy kan ook te eniger tyd 'n handmatige rugsteun aktiveer:\n"
"1. Gaan na die Eksterne Rugsteun-instellingsbladsy (Inproppe > Eksterne Rugsteun)\n"
"2. Kies rugsteuntipe (Slegs Databasis of Volle Rugsteun)\n"
"3. Klik 'Rugsteun na WebDAV Nou'\n"
"\n"
"Slegs Databasis-rugsteune is kleiner en vinniger. Volle rugsteune sluit opgelaaide foto's in."

#. plugin:google-analytics:section:1:content
#: 
msgid "• Page views and navigation patterns\n"
"• Session duration and engagement\n"
"• User demographics (if enabled in GA4)\n"
"• Device and browser information"
msgstr "• Bladsybesoeke en navigasiepatrone\n"
"• Sessieduur en betrokkenheid\n"
"• Gebruikersdemografie (indien geaktiveer in GA4)\n"
"• Toestel- en blaaierinligting"

