#: 
msgid "Create a full backup of your church database. Download a database-only SQL file or a complete archive including uploaded photos."
msgstr "Skep 'n volledige rugsteun van u kerklêer. Laai 'n slegs-databasis-SQL-lêer of 'n volledige argief insluitend opgelaaide foto's af."

