#: 
msgid "Export congregation data to CSV format. Choose which fields to include and filter by classification, group, gender, and more."
msgstr "Voer gemeentedata uit na CSV-formaat. Kies watter velde om in te sluit en filtreer per klassifikasie, groep, geslag en meer."

#: 
msgid "Export all people in the format expected by ChMeetings, making it easy to sync your congregation data with the ChMeetings platform."
msgstr "Voer alle persone uit in die formaat wat deur ChMeetings verwag word, sodat u gemeentedata maklik met die ChMeetings-platform gesinkroniseer kan word."

#: 
msgid "Export your church data to various formats"
msgstr "Voer u kerkdata uit na verskeie formate"

#: 
msgid "External (WebDAV) backup via plugin"
msgstr "Eksterne (WebDAV) rugsteun via inprop"

#: 
msgid "Family or individual record layout"
