msgstr "E-pos is gedeaktiveer"

#: 
msgid "Email is disabled. Configure email before resetting passwords, or use Change Password."
msgstr "E-pos is gedeaktiveer. Stel e-pos op voor wagwoordterugstelling, of gebruik Verander wagwoord."

#: 
msgid "Email is disabled. Enable it in the Email Dashboard settings before testing."
msgstr "E-pos is gedeaktiveer. Aktiveer dit in die E-pos-paneelbord-instellings voor toetsing."

#: 
msgid "Enter one of your backup recovery codes"
msgstr "Voer een van u rugsteun-herstelkodes in"

#: 
msgid "Enter one of your backup recovery codes to access your account"
msgstr "Voer een van u rugsteun-herstelkodes in om toegang tot u rekening te kry"

#: 
msgid "Existing Options"
msgstr "Bestaande opsies"

#: 
msgid "Group not found for this role list"
msgstr "Groep nie gevind vir hierdie rollys nie"

#: 
msgid "Inactive status can only be toggled for the classifications list"
msgstr "Inaktiewe status kan slegs vir die klassifikasielys omgeskakel word"

#: 
msgid "New users will not receive a welcome email with their credentials. Share the password with them manually, or configure email first."
msgstr "Nuwe gebruikers sal nie 'n welkome e-pos met hul geloofsbriewe ontvang nie. Deel die wagwoord handmatig met hulle, of stel eers e-pos op."

#: 
msgid "Option name is required"
msgstr "Opsienaam is verpligtend"

#: 
msgid "Option not found"
msgstr "Opsie nie gevind nie"

#: 
msgid "Optional short summary shown as inbox preview text beside the subject line. Leave blank to let the email client auto-generate from the body. Per-email types (password reset, new member, verification) set their own preheader; this is a fallback."
msgstr "Opsionele kort opsomming wat as voorskoutableks langs die onderwerplyn vertoon word. Laat leeg om die e-poskliënt outomaties uit die liggaam te genereer. Per-e-postipes (wagwoordterugstelling, nuwe lid, verifikasie) stel hul eie vooropskrif in; dit is 'n terugvalopsie."

#: 
msgid "Password reset emails and new-account welcome emails will not be sent until email is configured. Users will not receive credentials automatically."
msgstr "Wagwoordterugstelling-e-posse en nuwe-rekening-welkome-e-posse sal nie gestuur word totdat e-pos opgestel is nie. Gebruikers sal nie outomaties geloofsbriewe ontvang nie."

#: 
msgid "Password reset is unavailable because email is disabled. Please contact your system administrator."
msgstr "Wagwoordterugstelling is nie beskikbaar nie omdat e-pos gedeaktiveer is. Kontak asseblief u stelseladministrateur."

#: 
msgid "Password was reset but the email could not be sent. The user is locked out — share the new password manually or use Change Password."
msgstr "Wagwoord is teruggestel maar die e-pos kon nie gestuur word nie. Die gebruiker is uitgesluit — deel die nuwe wagwoord handmatig of gebruik Verander wagwoord."

